title: Kirk Minihane Is Back at Barstool HQ
description:
Kirk Minihane is back in New York City, but he's not sure why. The boys break down their wonderful experience getting to NYC and the next few days at Barstool HQ. Plus, debriefing the Gerry Callahan episode, more prank calls, and more academic hysteria over The Joker. Jared Carrabis hops on at the end.Â
